Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:34.23,Spica - Title,,0,0,90,,Campanella's Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.18,0:24:36.14,Spica - Title,,0,0,90,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.24,0:25:00.06,Spica - Title,,0,0,90,,Even Underwater, There Is Space
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:57.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Our country's first manned exploratory space rocket, the Lion, was launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:04.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,However, 72 seconds after liftoff…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:07.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,…the liquid fuel booster suddenly exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,And although the Space Control Center activated what could be called its self-destruct system…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,…the flight suspension system did not function correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:24.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The Lion fell into an urban area and caused a huge disaster with many civilian casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Five years later…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:56.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}You're the girl from that mansion in the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}Can't you tell by looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}It's a rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}A rocket-shaped secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:17.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}Can I come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}I won't tell anyone about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}If you don't tell anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,{\be1}Would you like to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.97,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Everyone, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:29.97,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Tomorrow is the Yuigahama Elementary\NSchool's annual hiking competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:35.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The first grade will climb up the Mitake mountain you see behind the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:39.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The safety guidelines are written on\Nthe sheet, so follow them properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Now, everyone be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.20,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hey, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm telling you to be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:01.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Anyway, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:15.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey, wait, all of you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Return to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Suzunari-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.32,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,What's wrong? You look so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:36.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Why did I think that I wanted to\Nbe an elementary school teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Don't tell me you're ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:44.25,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I'm sort of losing my confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:51.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The teachers from Kitachuu are having a party this Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Won't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:57.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You always skip these things, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.85,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,There'll be nice guys there, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:13.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,This is a birthday cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:22.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You've loved big strawberry cakes since you were a kid, right, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:27.13,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Stop treating me like a child all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm already twenty-four now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Twenty-four, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It seems so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:42.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You used to be this tiny and were such a cry-baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.77,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,...but now you're already twenty-four...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.61,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Yuuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,How long are you going to fuss over this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What do you mean, "this town"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.21,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,You still can't forget about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:07.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's not a bad thing to hold on to your feelings for another...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:11.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...but he is someone who has already died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:15.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Isn't it time you looked toward the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:19.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,It's been five years since the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Isn't that long enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.07,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Come back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Dad, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:32.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Your mother's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:36.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,To have you married and taking over our shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:40.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's what your mother hopes for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:45.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,If you can, can you set your mother's mind at ease?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.64,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Forget it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.81,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,About the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.52,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,About him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.56,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,Yuigahama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.52,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,Yep, the town where I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.03,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,It's a place where the sea and the mountains look really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.37,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,The mountains were like the kids' territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.03,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,I even had a secret hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:24.58,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,At bad times, or hard times. I'd go there and look at the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:30.00,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,When I'd do that. I'd mysteriously feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:34.55,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,Compared to the tens of thousands of light\Nyears between here and the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:40.01,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,...I realized that my own troubles were very tiny things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:43.60,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,I can get closer to those stars soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.03,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,My dreams are coming true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Everyone gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:15.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Now, everyone in the first grade, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You will now be split into groups to go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:25.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,While you're looking for signs with bird marks, try your hardest and try to get the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:29.81,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Do not wander off by yourself under any circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:34.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Why did I end up with you, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:37.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Now, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:02.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Let's see, number three, the password is "sun"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Let's go to the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:06.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,See, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.98,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,You're right! It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.86,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hey, Asumi-chan, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.11,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:23.95,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,They said if you find all ten bird marks, you get to have a memorial medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's why the boys are so enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,What about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:33.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But my brother said it was probably impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:33.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We should go and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:38.51,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Only one person has ever gotten the medal he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:42.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I have found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.85,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,You've done a good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Number six, the password is "Jupiter".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,"Jupiter"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,All right, that's five!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey! You guys are too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.99,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,That's why girls are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Be quiet already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.53,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,All right! Found the ninth one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.83,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Awesome! Just one more left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The tenth one isn't around here anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:19.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Did I miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Asumi-chan! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Really... what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We'll leave you behind, Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Huh? What do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The sound of a harmonica...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Huh? Are you a dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:44.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Why would you hear a harmonica\Nin the middle of the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I hear it! Lion-san's harmonica!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,H-Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:52.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Fuchuuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:03.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Suzunari-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:06.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What's the meaning of this, Suzunari-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:12.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,A girl and a boy from my class went into\Nthe woods and haven't returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I told you to watch the students closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:17.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,In any case, let's split up and search for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.32,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,It something happens, it'll be your responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:06.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's a rocket!
Comment: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:27.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.56,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:38.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I've lost the confidence to continue working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:41.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's very unlike you, Suzunari-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,A lot of things happen when you're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:48.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Try and remember why you started this work in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'll return this to you for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.83,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:02.04,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I don't know what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.63,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I'm lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.01,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,...and empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.76,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,It feels like I'm being crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Fuchuuya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.90,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Help me... Takano-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.58,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I miss you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.00,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:55.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Fuchuuya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Where's Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I lost her somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:08.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,She's a dummy, but she runs really fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So which way did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Let's see... that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Or maybe it was this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Huh? Maybe it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Which way is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:23.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Even if you yell at me, I don't know! I just don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:26.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Sensei, haven't you been a bit hysterical lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:33.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,In any case, let's look for Asumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.42,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.22,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,A railroad track?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:18.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I don't remember a train going through here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,No, this is a discontinued line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,They aren't used anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.02,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:31.49,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Why do I know this, when I've never been here before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.61,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Which way are we going to look now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:39.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Let's see... let's try going further into the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:47.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's like a mummy hunter turning into a mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:47.67,Spica - Notes,,0,0,90,,Note: A quote used when one goes out looking\Nfor someone, but does not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:51.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I don't think that dummy would die easily, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.86,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Fuchuuya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.36,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Let's rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I ran out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I'm so unlucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:04.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Nothing good comes from being involved with Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Here, I'll give you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:08.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:15.15,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,How did I know about this discontinued line?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.20,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,There's this railroad track that isn't used...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.87,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,That's right, Takano-kun was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.37,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,There's this railroad track that isn't used.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.33,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,It travels straight through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:31.55,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,I made a secret base there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:36.01,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,Every day I went there, untiringly taking plywood and iron plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.93,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,A rocket-shaped secret headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,We're going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You go and take a look at the right side!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:52.11,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Geez, you're such a slave driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Aren't you a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:36.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You know you'll get lost in a forest like this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:41.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I heard the sound of a harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's because I wanted to see Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:52.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Lion-san disappeared, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:58.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I was waiting and waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:06.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I see, you want to see Lion-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But that person's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.48,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Ah, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's the hiking competition memorial medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:22.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,That was inside that treasure box.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Treasure box?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:40.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:44.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Dummy! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:53.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,"When I grow up..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:02.20,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,"When I grow up, I want to be an {space}astronaut."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.87,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,90,,I want to be an {space}astronaut...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:10.70,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,"I want to see the same blue Earth that Gagarin saw."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:15.08,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,"From the window of the rocket in outer space..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:23.76,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,"...I want to see Yuigahama and the Yuigahama fireworks that I like."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.77,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,That is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.36,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,...my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.53,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Hello? Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.49,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:51.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I can't go back to Tokyo after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:57.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,I've already sorted out my feelings about that accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Yeah, give my regards to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.88,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.81,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Yoshida-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:17.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Are there really going to be nice guys at today's party?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:24.61,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,I want to try living with lots and lots of children with the light of their dreams sparkling in their earnest eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:29.32,Spica - Italic,,0,0,90,,Takano-kun, that is my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.46,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Ah, it was over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:37.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,The tenth mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.46,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Good job finding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:50.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You still haven't fulfilled your promise, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:52.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,My promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,You're going to take me on your rocket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:58.56,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,90,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.76,0:24:36.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,It's the first time we're trying on the space suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.72,0:24:40.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,But, I'm shocked because there aren't any sizes that fit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.43,0:24:45.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,This is a problem, and Sano-sensei's trying to make me quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.48,0:24:49.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,On the other hand, Marika-chan is still stubborn,\Nand is always fighting with Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.98,0:24:53.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,...even though no one can go to space by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:57.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,90,,Next time on Twin Spica: Even Underwater, There Is Space.